WEBVTT

00:01.422 --> 00:02.833
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:02.833 --> 00:04.085
I WANT TO MAKE YOU A LOT
OF MONEY, LOUISE. TRUST ME.

00:04.085 --> 00:06.297
Margaux: YOUR MOTHER
CAME TO SEE ME LAST NIGHT.

00:06.297 --> 00:07.888
WHAT DID SHE WANT?
 A LOAN.

00:07.888 --> 00:09.180
NOW SHE OWES ME.

00:09.180 --> 00:10.841
Ben: DID YOU GET A LOOK
AT HIS FACE?

00:10.841 --> 00:12.973
I COULD BARELY
MAKE OUT ANYTHING

00:12.973 --> 00:14.435
BEFORE HE JUMPED
OFF THE BALCONY.

00:14.435 --> 00:17.518
Alvarez: IT IS TRUE
THAT DAVID CLARKE IS ALIVE.

00:17.518 --> 00:18.599
EM.

00:18.599 --> 00:19.810
Ben: ARE YOU READY
TO MAKE AN I.D.?

00:19.810 --> 00:20.981
No.

00:20.981 --> 00:22.903
CONRAD GRAYSON
FAKED MY DEATH,

00:22.903 --> 00:24.275
AND THEN
HE LOCKED ME AWAY.

00:24.275 --> 00:27.648
WE ASK FOR PRIVACY SO THAT
DAVID CAN BE WITH HIS FAMILY.

00:27.648 --> 00:29.950
SHE GOT TO HIM FIRST.

00:39.960 --> 00:43.043
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING,
REPORTERS TALKING INDISTINCTLY ]

00:47.758 --> 00:49.840
YOU WERE RIGHT.

00:49.840 --> 00:52.052
THEY'RE NOT
GONNA LEAVE ME ALONE.

00:52.052 --> 00:54.054
WHICH IS WHY I DIDN'T
WANT YOU TO COME HERE.

00:54.054 --> 00:55.886
I NEEDED TO SEE IT
FOR MYSELF.

00:55.886 --> 00:57.978
I'M NOT FIGHTING WITH YOU,
DAVID.

00:57.978 --> 01:01.102
I'M SIMPLY CONCERNED
FOR YOU.

01:01.102 --> 01:04.355
STILL EDGY
AFTER THE FBI DEBRIEFINGS.

01:04.355 --> 01:06.447
IT WASN'T EASY
GOING OVER THE PAST 10 YEARS.

01:06.447 --> 01:09.900
I'M SO SORRY
YOU HAD TO ENDURE THAT.

01:09.900 --> 01:11.572
I'M GRATEFUL THAT YOU --

01:11.572 --> 01:13.994
THAT YOU WERE IN D.C. WITH ME
THIS WEEK...

01:13.994 --> 01:15.576
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

01:15.576 --> 01:17.538
...AND FOR CONFIRMING
WHAT I SAID.

01:17.538 --> 01:19.250
Reporter:
THEY'RE ON THE MOVE.

01:19.250 --> 01:21.252
NO ONE WILL EVER KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED TO CONRAD.

01:21.252 --> 01:22.913
I PROMISE, DAVID.

01:22.913 --> 01:25.005
CAN YOU IMAGINE THE HEADLINES
IF THEY DID?

01:25.005 --> 01:28.008
AND WE THOUGHT WE'D CREATE
A SCANDAL RUNNING AWAY TOGETHER.

01:28.008 --> 01:28.969
REMEMBER?

01:28.969 --> 01:31.262
SEEMS LIKE
A LIFETIME AGO.

01:31.262 --> 01:32.383
YES, IT DOES.

01:32.383 --> 01:34.975
I USED TO THINK ABOUT
THAT DAY ON THE BEACH.

01:34.975 --> 01:38.849
IT HELPED KEEP ME SANE
WHEN I WAS...ABOUT TO BREAK.

01:38.849 --> 01:40.020
[ CAR DOOR OPENS ]

01:40.020 --> 01:44.145
I USED TO IMAGINE OUR LIFE
IF WE HAD GOTTEN AWAY.

01:44.145 --> 01:45.816
THIS TIME, WE WILL.

01:47.107 --> 01:48.989
I PROMISE.

01:50.281 --> 01:52.993
[ GRUNTING, PANTING ]

01:52.993 --> 01:54.615
HEY. EMILY.

01:54.615 --> 01:56.157
THOSE MAY BE
FISTS OF FURY,

01:56.157 --> 01:58.579
BUT THEY'RE STILL
MADE OF FLESH AND BONE.

01:58.579 --> 01:59.830
GO EASY.

01:59.830 --> 02:02.122
FIVE DAYS, I'VE BEEN FORCED
TO WATCH MY FATHER ON TV

02:02.122 --> 02:03.624
WHILE VICTORIA
HASN'T LEFT HIS SIDE.

02:03.624 --> 02:06.006
YEAH, AND IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT
THAT SHE GOT TO HIM FIRST.

02:06.006 --> 02:08.088
IS THAT SUPPOSED TO
MAKE ME FEEL BETTER?

02:08.088 --> 02:10.751
I KNOW HOW FRAGILE
A PERSON'S MIND IS

02:10.751 --> 02:12.213
AFTER ENDURING
THAT KIND OF TORTURE.

02:12.213 --> 02:13.964
IT'S EXACTLY
THE KIND OF LEVERAGE

02:13.964 --> 02:16.257
VICTORIA NEEDS
TO MANIPULATE HIM.

02:16.257 --> 02:18.018
[ GRUNTING ]

02:18.018 --> 02:21.262
AND...THEY JUST GOT BACK
FROM D.C.

02:21.262 --> 02:24.435
SHE TOOK HIM
TO AMANDA'S GRAVE?

02:24.435 --> 02:25.436
EMS --

02:25.436 --> 02:26.687
LOOK AT WHAT SHE'S DOING,
NOLAN!

02:26.687 --> 02:28.148
WE HAVE TO GET HIM
AWAY FROM HER.

02:28.148 --> 02:30.030
[ VELCRO RIPS ]
 YEAH, I KNOW,
AND IT PISSES ME OFF, TOO.

02:30.030 --> 02:31.151
HE WAS LIKE A FATHER
TO ME.

02:31.151 --> 02:32.733
[ GLOVES THUD ]
 HE IS MY FATHER.

02:32.733 --> 02:35.155
AND HE CLEARLY
DOESN'T KNOW THAT,

02:35.155 --> 02:36.947
WHICH MEANS
SHE HASN'T TOLD HIM.

02:36.947 --> 02:38.118
[ SIGHS ]

02:38.118 --> 02:40.331
I MEAN, WE DON'T KNOW WHAT ANGLE
VICTORIA IS PLAYING YET.

02:40.331 --> 02:41.622
I'LL TAKE THE RISK.

02:41.622 --> 02:43.994
THE LAST TIME YOU WERE IN A ROOM
WITH YOUR FATHER,

02:43.994 --> 02:45.085
HE TRIED TO KILL YOU.

02:45.085 --> 02:46.417
HE WASN'T COMING FOR ME,
NOLAN.

02:46.417 --> 02:48.168
HE WAS PROBABLY LOOKING
FOR CONRAD.

02:48.168 --> 02:49.340
PROBABLY.

02:49.340 --> 02:53.093
BUT IT STILL PROVES THAT HE IS
NOT THE MAN THAT HE ONCE WAS.

02:53.093 --> 02:57.007
EMILY, WHAT IF IT'S WORSE
THAN WE THINK?

02:57.007 --> 02:58.679
WHAT IF
CONRAD DID BREAK HIM?

02:58.679 --> 03:01.222
[ SIGHS ]

03:01.222 --> 03:03.474
Reporter:
JACK, ANY WORD FROM DAVID?

03:03.474 --> 03:05.476
HAVE YOU TALKED
TO YOUR FATHER-IN-LAW YET?

03:05.476 --> 03:07.518
GUYS, STAY ON THE SIDEWALK.
I GOT A KID INSIDE.

03:07.518 --> 03:09.189
WHEN IS DAVID GONNA MEET
HIS GRANDSON?

03:09.189 --> 03:10.861
ARE YOU AFRAID
HE'S UPSET WITH YOU

03:10.861 --> 03:12.112
FOR NOT PROTECTING
AMANDA?

03:12.112 --> 03:15.155
DO YOU THINK HE BLAMES YOU
FOR THE DEATH OF HIS DAUGHTER?

03:16.697 --> 03:19.159
GET THE HELL OFF
MY PROPERTY NOW!

03:19.159 --> 03:21.662
NOW! BOTH OF YOU!

03:21.662 --> 03:23.824
[ CAR DOORS OPEN ]

03:24.955 --> 03:27.127
VICTORIA, IT'S MARGAUX AGAIN.

03:27.127 --> 03:29.420
I UNDERSTAND YOU DO NOT WISH
TO SPEAK WITH THE MEDIA,

03:29.420 --> 03:32.423
BUT WE ARE FAMILY,
SO PLEASE -- TRUST ME.

03:32.423 --> 03:34.044
CALL ME BACK.

03:34.044 --> 03:36.257
YOU WON'T HEAR
FROM HER.

03:36.257 --> 03:38.509
SHE'S GONNA KEEP WORKING
THIS THREE-RING CIRCUS

03:38.509 --> 03:41.141
LIKE P.T. BARNUM
IN STILETTOS.

03:41.141 --> 03:43.934
WHILE I WATCH FROM THE STANDS
ALONG WITH EVERYONE ELSE --

03:43.934 --> 03:47.147
DESPITE THE FACT
THAT SHE OWES ME

03:47.147 --> 03:49.019
AND, NOT TO MENTION,
OUR CONNECTION.

03:49.019 --> 03:50.271
YEAH, A CONNECTION
NO ONE KNOWS ABOUT.

03:50.271 --> 03:53.734
TAKE MY ADVICE --
KEEP IT THAT WAY.

03:53.734 --> 03:55.856
WHY?

03:55.856 --> 03:59.280
WHAT HAPPENED WITH DAVID
WAS CONRAD'S CRIME, NOT YOURS.

03:59.280 --> 04:01.362
TO THE PUBLIC,
WE GRAYSONS ARE ALL THE SAME.

04:01.362 --> 04:03.163
WHY DO YOU THINK
I HAVEN'T BEEN ABLE

04:03.163 --> 04:05.496
TO LAND A CLIENT,
OTHER THAN LOUISE ELLIS?

04:05.496 --> 04:07.127
I CAN HELP YOU, DANIEL.

04:07.127 --> 04:09.750
TELL YOUR SIDE,
CHANGE PEOPLE'S OPINIONS.

04:09.750 --> 04:11.001
NO, NO, NO.
NO PRESS.

04:11.001 --> 04:13.294
I HAVE TO DO THIS
 MY WAY.

04:13.294 --> 04:15.836
LISTEN,
WHEN I WAS WITH EMILY,

04:15.836 --> 04:18.379
WE LIVED IN THE HEADLINES,
AND THAT WAS A MISTAKE.

04:18.379 --> 04:20.089
THE LESS PEOPLE KNOW
ABOUT YOU,

04:20.089 --> 04:23.934
THE MORE CONTROL YOU HAVE
OVER YOUR OWN LIFE.

04:23.934 --> 04:27.187
IS THAT WHY YOU'RE SO SECRETIVE
ABOUT THIS LOUISE GIRL?

04:27.187 --> 04:28.649
YEAH. I CAN'T AFFORD
TO BLOW THIS.

04:28.649 --> 04:31.061
SHE'S THAT VALUABLE?

04:31.061 --> 04:33.153
I'M STILL COUNTING THE ZEROES
IN HER PORTFOLIO.

04:33.153 --> 04:34.775
AND BY SOME MIRACLE,

04:34.775 --> 04:37.358
SHE CHOSE ME
 TO HANDLE HER ACCOUNT.

04:37.358 --> 04:40.070
AND I JUST GOT TO PROVE
THAT SHE DIDN'T MAKE A MISTAKE.

04:40.070 --> 04:43.664
THEN YOU KNOW
WHAT YOU MUST DO --

04:43.664 --> 04:45.245
KEEP HER HAPPY.

04:49.289 --> 04:52.002
[ REPORTERS TALKING
INDISTINCTLY ]

04:52.002 --> 04:54.124
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

05:00.591 --> 05:04.014
[ CAR DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

05:19.239 --> 05:21.702
[ TIRES SQUEAL, ENGINE REVS ]

05:22.993 --> 05:23.944
DAVID!

05:23.944 --> 05:25.075
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

05:29.370 --> 05:31.372
Reporter: SOMEONE JUST TRIED
TO RUN OVER DAVID CLARKE.

05:31.372 --> 05:34.415
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

05:44.174 --> 05:45.726
DAVID!

06:04.825 --> 06:06.286
DO THEY KNOW
WHO DID THIS?

06:06.286 --> 06:07.658
NO. NO.

06:07.658 --> 06:09.369
THEY FOUND THE CAR
THREE BLOCKS AWAY.

06:09.369 --> 06:11.121
IT WAS STOLEN.
IT'S A DEAD END.

06:11.121 --> 06:12.913
THEY'VE OFFERED ME
POLICE PROTECTION

06:12.913 --> 06:14.124
UNTIL THEY CATCH THE GUY.

06:15.626 --> 06:18.048
DAVID, WE MUST GET YOU
TO SAFETY.

06:18.048 --> 06:19.590
NOW, I'VE ALREADY TALKED
TO A FRIEND OF MINE

06:19.590 --> 06:21.462
WHO HAS AN ESTATE
IN MARYLAND,

06:21.462 --> 06:23.884
NO, I'M NOT
GOING ANYWHERE.
 AND THEY'RE WILLING
TO ALLOW US TO USE IT, DAVID.

06:23.884 --> 06:25.345
WHY WOULD YOU STAY HERE?
IT'S NOT SAFE.

06:25.345 --> 06:27.468
ALL THESE STORIES I HEAR
ABOUT AMANDA --

06:27.468 --> 06:29.179
NOTHING REALLY
MAKES SENSE.

06:29.179 --> 06:30.891
I'D GONE TO HER GRAVE TODAY
HOPING FOR SOME CLOSURE,

06:30.891 --> 06:32.312
AND IT JUST RAISED
MORE QUESTIONS.

06:34.014 --> 06:35.145
I FEAR YOU WON'T LIKE
THE ANSWERS.

06:35.145 --> 06:37.568
I DON'T CARE.

06:37.568 --> 06:40.861
I AM GONNA FIND OUT
WHAT REALLY HAPPENED TO MY GIRL.

06:41.982 --> 06:44.074
Emily: VICTORIA WAS BEHIND THIS.
I'M SURE OF IT.

06:44.074 --> 06:46.286
SHE'S TERRIFIED THAT MY FATHER
WILL LEARN THE TRUTH ABOUT HER,

06:46.286 --> 06:47.788
SO SHE PUT A POLICE LINE
BETWEEN US.

06:47.788 --> 06:51.331
WELL, IT DEFINITELY SOUNDS LIKE
HER SHADE OF BITCH.

06:51.331 --> 06:53.704
WHICH IS WHY
YOU HAVE TO BE EXTRA-CAREFUL,

06:53.704 --> 06:56.747
BECAUSE NOW THE HOTEL
IS CRAWLING WITH COPS AND PRESS.

06:56.747 --> 06:57.958
YOU THINK
THAT'S GONNA STOP ME?

06:57.958 --> 07:00.040
YOU KNOW WHAT?

07:00.040 --> 07:04.004
MAYBE IF AIDEN WERE HERE,
HE COULD MAKE YOU SEE IT.

07:04.004 --> 07:07.468
BUT HE'S NOT,
SO YOU HAVE TO LISTEN TO ME.

07:07.468 --> 07:09.429
VICTORIA'S GUNNING FOR YOU,

07:09.429 --> 07:11.642
AND SHE'S THOUGHT
ALL OF THIS THROUGH

07:11.642 --> 07:14.645
WITH THE SAME PRECISION
YOU USUALLY DO.

07:14.645 --> 07:17.558
SO BEFORE YOU MAKE A MISTAKE,
SLOW DOWN.

07:17.558 --> 07:18.979
I CAN'T, OKAY?

07:18.979 --> 07:20.440
DON'T YOU UNDERSTAND,
NOLAN?

07:20.440 --> 07:21.942
I NEVER WENT TO SEE HIM
IN PRISON.

07:21.942 --> 07:24.655
ALL OF THESE YEARS, HE BELIEVED
THAT HIS DAUGHTER HATED HIM,

07:24.655 --> 07:26.827
AND I'VE LIVED WITH THAT GUILT
EVERY SINGLE DAY.

07:26.827 --> 07:28.569
NOW I HAVE THE CHANCE
TO MAKE IT RIGHT,

07:28.569 --> 07:30.070
TO LET HIM KNOW THAT
HIS DAUGHTER STILL LOVES HIM,

07:30.070 --> 07:31.492
SO PLEASE,
STOP FIGHTING ME.

07:32.743 --> 07:33.744
[ SIGHS ]

07:33.744 --> 07:35.786
OF COURSE.

07:35.786 --> 07:37.247
OF COURSE, KIDDO.

07:37.247 --> 07:39.249
I'M SORRY.

07:39.249 --> 07:40.501
IT'S JUST...

07:40.501 --> 07:43.133
VICKY'S DONE A HELL OF A JOB
CLARKE-BLOCKING US.

07:43.133 --> 07:48.088
ONLY FAMILY CAN GET THROUGH,
AND...YOU DON'T QUALIFY.

07:48.088 --> 07:49.259
AT LEAST, NOT YET.

07:55.185 --> 07:58.098
[ MAN TALKING INDISTINCTLY
ON P.A. ]

07:58.098 --> 07:59.980
PORTER. GO HOME.

08:01.522 --> 08:03.604
BUT I'M ON THE ROSTER.

08:06.156 --> 08:07.868
THIS IS ABOUT DAVID CLARKE,
ISN'T IT?

08:07.868 --> 08:10.490
TOUGH TO DO YOUR JOB
WHEN REPORTERS ARE TAILING YOU.

08:10.490 --> 08:14.164
I NEED YOU TO SIT THIS ONE
OUT -- JUST TILL IT BLOWS OVER.

08:14.164 --> 08:16.456
YEAH. SURE, CHIEF.

08:17.998 --> 08:19.580
I SAW YOU GOT AMBUSHED
THIS MORNING.

08:19.580 --> 08:20.711
[ SCOFFS ]

08:20.711 --> 08:22.462
YOU ALL RIGHT?

08:22.462 --> 08:24.464
I'M DYING
TO GET OUT THERE TODAY.

08:24.464 --> 08:26.547
CAN'T STAND SITTING AROUND,
FEELING USELESS.

08:26.547 --> 08:28.549
IMAGINE ALL THIS
HAS GOT TO BRING UP

08:28.549 --> 08:30.090
SOME PRETTY HEAVY STUFF
FOR YOU, YEAH?

08:30.090 --> 08:33.303
IT'S ALWAYS THERE
IN THE BACK OF MY MIND,

08:33.303 --> 08:36.015
BUT NOW EVERY JERK
WITH A MICROPHONE'S
ASKING ME ABOUT IT.

08:36.015 --> 08:38.058
"WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR BROTHER,
TO AMANDA?"

08:38.058 --> 08:40.981
HOW DID YOU MAKE IT THROUGH
ALL THAT?

08:42.022 --> 08:43.943
I ALMOST DIDN'T.

08:43.943 --> 08:47.027
FOR A WHILE, I THOUGHT
THAT GOD HAD IT OUT FOR ME.

08:47.027 --> 08:48.488
TURNS OUT,
IT WASN'T GOD AT ALL --

08:48.488 --> 08:49.990
JUST A MAN
WHO THOUGHT HE WAS,

08:49.990 --> 08:52.112
NOT GIVING A DAMN
ABOUT WHO HE HURT OR WHO DIED.

08:52.112 --> 08:54.114
[ LOCKER DOOR SLAMS ]

08:54.114 --> 08:56.246
SON OF A BITCH
GOT WHAT HE DESERVED.

08:56.246 --> 08:59.660
WELL, THE WORLD SEEMS TO AGREE
WITH YOU, BUT STILL...

08:59.660 --> 09:02.212
I MEAN, A CASE THAT HIGH-PROFILE
JUST GATHERING DUST?

09:02.212 --> 09:03.834
IT'S A LITTLE WEIRD,
DON'T YOU THINK?

09:03.834 --> 09:06.046
WELL, MAYBE IT'S 'CAUSE PEOPLE
CAN SEE IT FOR WHAT IT IS --

09:06.046 --> 09:07.588
JUSTICE.

09:11.471 --> 09:13.093
[ BELLS JINGLE ]

09:13.093 --> 09:16.346
[ MID-TEMPO POP MUSIC PLAYING
ON STEREO ]

09:18.979 --> 09:21.892
AH! DANNY!
YOU MADE IT!

09:23.063 --> 09:25.105
IS THIS YOUR FIRST
BUSINESS MEETING
IN A DRESS SHOP?

09:25.105 --> 09:27.487
[ CHUCKLES ] PRETTY --
PRETTY SURE IT IS, YEAH.

09:27.487 --> 09:28.649
ALTHOUGH, NEXT TIME,

09:28.649 --> 09:31.111
YOU MIGHT WANT TO CHOOSE
SOMEPLACE MORE PRIVATE.

09:31.111 --> 09:33.363
MY FAMILY IS STILL
THE TOP STORY.

09:33.363 --> 09:35.535
THEY DON'T BOTHER ME.

09:35.535 --> 09:37.157
I'M FROM THE SOUTH,
DEAR.

09:37.157 --> 09:39.830
IF THEY'RE NOT GOSSIPIN'
ABOUT YOU,

09:39.830 --> 09:42.332
YOU MIGHT AS WELL
BE DEAD.

09:42.332 --> 09:46.086
MAYBE I LIKE TO MAINTAIN
A LITTLE MYSTERY ABOUT MYSELF.

09:46.086 --> 09:48.208
WELL, I'M STILL TRYING
TO FIGURE YOU OUT,

09:48.208 --> 09:50.921
SO MISSION ACCOMPLISHED.

09:50.921 --> 09:54.134
WHICH PART ARE YOU TRYING
TO F-FIGURE OUT, EXACTLY?

09:54.134 --> 09:55.425
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

09:55.425 --> 09:58.598
WELL, YOU AND YOUR MAMA,
FOR STARTERS.

09:58.598 --> 09:59.890
WHY THE FEUD?

09:59.890 --> 10:01.181
OH, THERE'S NO MYSTERY.

10:01.181 --> 10:02.983
SHE'S A CONTROL FREAK.

10:02.983 --> 10:04.394
I GOT TIRED OF HER

10:04.394 --> 10:06.817
INJECTING HERSELF
INTO EVERY ASPECT OF MY LIFE.

10:06.817 --> 10:09.730
HMM.
EVEN YOUR LOVE LIFE?

10:09.730 --> 10:11.191
ESPECIALLY THAT.
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:11.191 --> 10:13.784
YOU WANT MY MOM'S ATTENTION,
DATE ME.

10:13.784 --> 10:15.946
NOTED.

10:19.199 --> 10:20.200
TOO MUCH?

10:21.081 --> 10:23.123
OR "HOT DAMN"?

10:23.123 --> 10:26.046
DEFINITELY "HOT DAMN."

10:28.749 --> 10:31.011
SO, TELL ME, DANNY,

10:31.011 --> 10:33.383
AM I WASTING ALL
MY TOP-NOTCH FLIRTING ON YOU?

10:33.383 --> 10:38.258
IS THERE A...PRIM NEW YORK GIRL
WAITING AT HOME?

10:40.721 --> 10:42.602
NO.

10:42.602 --> 10:44.975
NO, THERE'S NOT.

10:44.975 --> 10:47.067
[ REPORTERS SHOUTING
"CHARLOTTE!" ]

10:47.067 --> 10:49.029
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

10:49.029 --> 10:52.032
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

10:54.274 --> 10:55.906
OF COURSE
 YOU'D BE HERE.

10:55.906 --> 10:57.077
I NEED YOUR HELP.

10:57.077 --> 10:58.328
WHY WOULD I EVER
HELP YOU?

10:58.328 --> 11:01.041
OUR PROBLEMS ARE NOT THE ISSUE
RIGHT NOW. OUR FATHER IS.

11:01.041 --> 11:03.954
PLEASE --
I NEED TO SEE HIM ALONE.

11:03.954 --> 11:07.087
WHY DON'T YOU JUST
SCALE THE BUILDING,
KNOCK DOWN THE DOOR?

11:07.087 --> 11:10.050
I DOUBT A LITTLE
POLICE BARRICADE CAN STOP YOU.

11:10.050 --> 11:12.172
I WOULD DO THAT,
BUT THAT'S NOT EXACTLY

11:12.172 --> 11:14.254
HOW I WANT TO REUNITE
WITH OUR FATHER.

11:14.254 --> 11:15.635
OH, I GET IT.

11:15.635 --> 11:17.637
SO YOU WANT ME TO PAVE THE WAY
FOR YOUR TRIUMPHANT RETURN.

11:17.637 --> 11:19.179
I THINK I'LL PASS.

11:19.179 --> 11:20.560
[ PUSHES BUTTON ]

11:20.560 --> 11:23.934
ARE YOU SURE YOU WANT TO SIDE
WITH YOUR MOTHER ON THIS?

11:23.934 --> 11:26.476
WHO DO YOU THINK
WAS BEHIND THE ATTACK TODAY?

11:26.476 --> 11:29.069
NO. SHE LOVES DAVID.
SHE WOULD NEVER HURT HIM.

11:29.069 --> 11:31.651
CHARLOTTE, YOU AND I BOTH KNOW
THAT YOUR MOTHER WOULD DO

11:31.651 --> 11:33.693
WHATEVER IT TAKES
TO GET WHAT SHE WANTS,

11:33.693 --> 11:35.866
INCLUDING PUTTING
OUR FATHER'S LIFE AT RISK.

11:35.866 --> 11:37.077
SHE IS MANIPULATING HIM.

11:37.077 --> 11:37.988
GOD, CHARLOTTE,

11:37.988 --> 11:40.660
SHE TOOK HIM TO WHAT WAS
SUPPOSED TO BE MY GRAVE.

11:40.660 --> 11:43.453
DO YOU KNOW HOW PAINFUL
THAT MUST HAVE BEEN FOR HIM?

11:43.453 --> 11:45.996
WE HAVE TO STOP HER.

11:45.996 --> 11:48.328
PLEASE. I JUST WANT
TO TELL HIM THE TRUTH.

11:55.756 --> 11:57.137
MOTHER, YOU NEED
TO TELL ME THE TRUTH.

11:57.137 --> 11:59.259
WERE YOU BEHIND
THE ATTACK ON DAVID?

11:59.259 --> 12:02.012
HOW COULD YOU THINK
I WOULD DO SUCH A THING?

12:02.012 --> 12:04.104
I DO NOT THREATEN
THE PEOPLE I LOVE

12:04.104 --> 12:05.395
TO GET WHAT I WANT.

12:05.395 --> 12:06.726
YOU ARE SO BLIND,

12:06.726 --> 12:08.608
YOU CAN'T EVEN SEE
YOU'RE USING HIM.

12:08.608 --> 12:11.481
YOU TOOK HIM TO THAT GRAVE?!
WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?!

12:11.481 --> 12:14.444
YOUR FATHER DEMANDED TO GO THERE
AGAINST MY WISHES.

12:14.444 --> 12:17.908
DO YOU THINK I ENJOY
WATCHING HIM SUFFER?

12:17.908 --> 12:20.570
THEN WHY NOT
JUST TELL HIM THE TRUTH?

12:20.570 --> 12:22.622
THAT'S ALL
EMILY WANTS TO DO.

12:22.622 --> 12:23.954
AH.

12:23.954 --> 12:25.665
EMILY. WELL.

12:25.665 --> 12:27.667
[ PEN CLACKS ]

12:28.959 --> 12:31.251
SHE IS MANIPULATING YOU,
CHARLOTTE.

12:31.251 --> 12:34.254
THAT IS WHAT SHE DOES --
SHE LIES.

12:34.254 --> 12:35.926
AND WHEN THAT DOESN'T WORK,

12:35.926 --> 12:38.929
SHE RESORTS
TO VIOLENCE AND FEAR.

12:38.929 --> 12:41.141
IF SHE'D ONLY TOLD ME THE TRUTH
WHEN SHE FIRST ARRIVED,

12:41.141 --> 12:43.053
THE GIRL IN THAT GRAVE
WOULD BE ALIVE TODAY,

12:43.053 --> 12:44.344
AND SO WOULD DECLAN.

12:44.344 --> 12:45.806
[ DOOR OPENS ]

12:45.806 --> 12:47.477
Officer: ALL RIGHT, MR. CLARKE.
I'LL BE RIGHT OUTSIDE.

12:47.477 --> 12:49.189
CHARLOTTE.
 OH. DAD.

12:49.189 --> 12:50.600
IT'S ALL RIGHT.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

12:52.602 --> 12:53.894
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

12:53.894 --> 12:55.275
CHARLOTTE,
WHAT IS IT?

12:57.607 --> 13:00.110
IF THERE'S, UH, SOMETHING
YOU NEED TO TELL ME, YOU CAN.

13:03.573 --> 13:06.116
ACTUALLY, DAD, THERE'S SOMEONE
YOU NEED TO MEET.

13:09.619 --> 13:12.963
I BECAME A COP
TO GET CONTROL OF MY LIFE.

13:12.963 --> 13:15.175
AND NOW I CAN FEEL IT ALL
SLIPPING AWAY AGAIN,

13:15.175 --> 13:16.046
AND I HATE THAT IT'S --

13:16.046 --> 13:19.379
MAN, I'M SORRY
I'M GOING ON LIKE THIS.

13:19.379 --> 13:22.422
YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY McMURPHY
IN THIS CUCKOO'S NEST.

13:22.422 --> 13:25.976
I MEAN, DAVID WAS THE FATHER
THAT I ALWAYS WANTED.

13:25.976 --> 13:29.019
WHEN I THOUGHT HE WAS KILLED,
I FELL APART.

13:29.019 --> 13:32.102
BUT NOW HE'S BACK,
AND THERE IS A PART OF ME

13:32.102 --> 13:34.604
THAT JUST [SIGHS]
WANTS TO GO TO HIM.

13:34.604 --> 13:35.986
WELL, EVERY PART OF ME

13:35.986 --> 13:38.648
WANTS TO STAY AS FAR AWAY
FROM HIM AS POSSIBLE.

13:38.648 --> 13:40.780
[ SIGHS ]
'CAUSE OF CARL?

13:40.780 --> 13:44.574
DAVID THINKS THAT MY SON
IS HIS GRANDCHILD.

13:44.574 --> 13:46.206
WHAT WOULD I EVEN SAY
TO HIM?

13:46.206 --> 13:49.039
I CAN'T IMAGINE LYING
ABOUT SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

13:51.121 --> 13:53.543
PERSONALLY, I'M GLAD
THE TRUTH'S FINALLY COMING OUT.

13:53.543 --> 13:55.795
I WISH I FELT THE SAME.

13:55.795 --> 13:56.957
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

13:56.957 --> 13:59.920
EMILY HAS BEEN SO FOCUSED
ON GETTING TO DAVID

13:59.920 --> 14:02.052
THAT SHE'S NOT THINKING THROUGH
ALL THE VARIABLES.

14:02.052 --> 14:04.054
WELL, CAN YOU BLAME HER?
IT'S HER FATHER.

14:04.054 --> 14:05.055
JACK, I KNOW.

14:05.055 --> 14:07.928
BUT...
I'M AFRAID SHE'S RUSHING

14:07.928 --> 14:10.680
TO MEET A MAN
THAT DOESN'T EXIST ANYMORE.

14:10.680 --> 14:13.103
AND I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THAT'S GONNA DO TO HER.

14:40.921 --> 14:42.302
HEY.
 [ PAPER CRUMPLES ]

14:42.302 --> 14:43.673
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

14:43.673 --> 14:45.055
ARE YOU SELLING ACCESS
TO DAVID CLARKE?

14:45.055 --> 14:47.267
MAYBE SNEAK IN A CAMERA,
GET SOME STOLEN FOOTAGE?

14:47.267 --> 14:50.010
UM, I'M SORRY.
I DIDN'T --
 GET OUT OF HERE.

14:53.103 --> 14:54.684
I EXPECT BETTER
FROM YOU.

14:54.684 --> 14:57.437
WHAT? YOU TRULY BELIEVE
OTHERS OUT THERE ARE
NOT DOING THE SAME?

14:57.437 --> 14:58.608
AND THAT
MAKES IT RIGHT?

14:58.608 --> 15:00.190
IT MAKES IT REALITY.

15:00.190 --> 15:02.232
YOU KNOW, SOME OF US
HAVE A JOB TO DO.

15:02.232 --> 15:04.784
THAT'S WHY I'M HERE,
BUT WHY ARE YOU?

15:04.784 --> 15:06.366
I AM FIGHTING
FOR AMANDA CLARKE.

15:06.366 --> 15:08.028
SHE WANTED
HER FATHER'S NAME CLEARED

15:08.028 --> 15:09.199
AND HER ENEMIES
BROUGHT TO JUSTICE,

15:09.199 --> 15:10.991
BUT WHAT SHE DIDN'T WANT

15:10.991 --> 15:12.993
WAS FOR HIM TO BE USED
BY PEOPLE LIKE YOU.

15:12.993 --> 15:14.794
[ CHUCKLES ]

15:14.794 --> 15:17.417
YOU SHOULD LEARN
TO GOVERN YOUR EMOTIONS, EMILY.

15:17.417 --> 15:20.040
THIS IS SUCH
AN UNFLATTERING COLOR ON YOU.

15:23.093 --> 15:25.095
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

15:31.051 --> 15:33.103
[ SIGHS SHAKILY ]

15:35.055 --> 15:37.477
PEOPLE THINK
THE SECRET'S IN THE COPPER MUG.

15:37.477 --> 15:39.319
IT'S ACTUALLY
THE EXTRA VODKA.

15:42.022 --> 15:45.275
TO...
GETTING WHAT YOU WANT.

15:45.275 --> 15:47.327
I'LL DRINK TO THAT,
NEIGHBOR.

15:47.327 --> 15:49.199
MM.
 TEMPORARY NEIGHBOR.

15:49.199 --> 15:51.871
I'M HAVING MY YACHT BROUGHT UP
FROM HILTON HEAD.

15:51.871 --> 15:54.284
A HOTEL'S NOT AN APPROPRIATE
PLACE TO CALL HOME.

15:54.284 --> 15:56.286
YOU CALLING ME
INAPPROPRIATE?

15:57.957 --> 15:59.539
WELL, I DON'T KNOW.

15:59.539 --> 16:03.003
BUT IT DOES REVEAL
QUITE A BIT ABOUT YOU.

16:03.003 --> 16:04.424
I MEAN,
LOOK AROUND, DANNY.

16:04.424 --> 16:07.297
NO PERSONAL ITEMS.

16:07.297 --> 16:09.469
NOTHING TO REMIND YOU
OF YOUR FAMILY

16:09.469 --> 16:11.971
OR WHERE YOU COME FROM.

16:11.971 --> 16:16.096
YOU ARE A MAN
IN SEARCH OF AN IDENTITY.

16:16.096 --> 16:20.060
AND YOU CLEARLY
HAVEN'T SETTLED ON ONE YET.

16:21.231 --> 16:23.653
YOU'RE UNLIKE
ANYONE I'VE EVER MET.

16:23.653 --> 16:26.366
WELL, MULTIPLE ROUNDS
OF ELECTROSHOCK THERAPY

16:26.366 --> 16:28.488
WILL DO THAT TO A GIRL.

16:28.488 --> 16:30.910
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

16:32.202 --> 16:34.874
I JUST HAVEN'T
FIGURED YOU OUT YET, EITHER.

16:34.874 --> 16:39.119
NOW, WHICH PART ARE YOU TRYING
TO FIGURE OUT, EXACTLY?

16:43.123 --> 16:44.624
IS SOMETHING THE MATTER?

16:44.624 --> 16:48.838
BECAUSE...
UNLESS I'M SORELY MISTAKEN,

16:48.838 --> 16:52.052
YOU'RE JUST AS ATTRACTED TO ME
AS I AM TO YOU.

16:55.975 --> 16:59.189
SO, TELL ME,
DANIEL GRAYSON...

16:59.189 --> 17:01.521
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

17:32.432 --> 17:34.013
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

17:34.013 --> 17:34.974
[ DOOR OPENS ]

17:37.177 --> 17:38.178
JACK.

17:38.178 --> 17:39.139
I THOUGHT IT WAS TIME

17:39.139 --> 17:41.391
DAVID WAS FINALLY REUNITED
WITH HIS SON-IN-LAW.

17:43.353 --> 17:45.855
HELLO, JACK.

17:45.855 --> 17:47.947
HEY.

17:47.947 --> 17:49.859
UH, COME IN.

17:59.249 --> 18:02.292
CHARLOTTE SAID
YOU WOULD BE JOINING ME.

18:02.292 --> 18:05.875
DO COME IN.
WE HAVE SO MUCH TO DISCUSS.

18:12.552 --> 18:13.973
WHERE THE HELL
IS MY FATHER?

18:13.973 --> 18:15.765
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

18:15.765 --> 18:19.639
AND WHAT EXACTLY IS YOUR PLAN
ONCE YOU DO FIND HIM, EMILY?

18:19.639 --> 18:21.060
YOU KNOW DAMN WELL,

18:21.060 --> 18:23.933
WHICH IS WHY YOU'RE SO DESPERATE
TO TURN HIM AGAINST ME.

18:23.933 --> 18:25.485
HMM.

18:25.485 --> 18:27.106
[ GLASS CLINKS ]

18:27.106 --> 18:29.729
I WILL NOT DESTROY
THE MEMORY OF HIS CHILD.

18:29.729 --> 18:33.112
YOU MAY HAVE THAT HONOR --
IF YOU TRULY ARE THAT CRUEL.

18:33.112 --> 18:34.364
[ SCOFFS ]

18:34.364 --> 18:37.036
YOU WANT TO TALK "CRUEL,"
VICTORIA?

18:37.036 --> 18:39.199
HOW ABOUT RIPPING A CHILD
AWAY FROM HER FATHER

18:39.199 --> 18:41.080
OR BRIBING A DOCTOR

18:41.080 --> 18:44.164
INTO POISONING EVERY GOOD MEMORY
SHE EVER HAD OF HIM?

18:44.164 --> 18:47.707
THAT IS THE TRUTH
THAT YOU'RE RUNNING FROM.

18:47.707 --> 18:49.629
NOW TELL ME
WHERE MY FATHER IS.

18:49.629 --> 18:51.211
OR YOU'LL WHAT?

18:51.211 --> 18:53.513
COME AFTER MY CHILDREN
AGAIN?

18:53.513 --> 18:56.386
OR AM I TO BE THE NEXT VICTIM
IN YOUR GROWING BODY COUNT?

18:56.386 --> 18:58.097
OH, THAT,
I COULD LIVE WITH.

18:58.097 --> 19:00.059
BUT COULD YOUR FATHER?

19:00.059 --> 19:02.182
HAVE YOU EVER CONSIDERED
WHAT WILL HAPPEN

19:02.182 --> 19:05.185
WHEN YOU TELL HIM
ABOUT ALL YOUR LIES

19:05.185 --> 19:09.439
OR THE DEATH YOU CAUSED
IN HIS NAME, HMM?

19:09.439 --> 19:11.191
I WONDER
WHAT HE'LL FEEL.

19:12.572 --> 19:14.113
GUILT?

19:14.113 --> 19:15.235
SHAME?

19:17.447 --> 19:21.491
YOUR PLAN WAS PERFECT, EMILY,
SAVE FOR ONE DETAIL --

19:21.491 --> 19:23.583
YOUR FATHER IS ALIVE.

19:25.084 --> 19:28.748
AND NOW YOU MUST LIVE
WITH THE REPERCUSSIONS
OF WHAT YOU'VE DONE.

19:28.748 --> 19:30.590
AND SO WILL YOU.

19:30.590 --> 19:32.212
I'LL MAKE SURE OF IT.

19:32.212 --> 19:33.843
THEN TELL HIM.

19:35.094 --> 19:38.097
OR STAY HIDDEN
IN THIS PATHETIC IDENTITY.

19:38.097 --> 19:41.891
EITHER WAY, IT WILL BE
TREMENDOUS FUN TO WATCH.

19:43.263 --> 19:45.895
YOU CAN
SHOW YOURSELF OUT.

19:48.067 --> 19:50.730
YOU KNOW WHAT I SEE?

19:50.730 --> 19:53.022
IS JUST
A FRIGHTENED WOMAN

19:53.022 --> 19:54.694
ABOUT TO LOSE
THE LAST PERSON

19:54.694 --> 19:58.117
SHE COULD EVER TRICK
INTO LOVING HER

19:58.117 --> 19:59.198
TO HIS DAUGHTER.

20:04.824 --> 20:05.995
[ DOOR OPENS ]

20:05.995 --> 20:09.879
DAVID, IT'S...REALLY GREAT
TO SEE YOU AGAIN,

20:09.879 --> 20:11.631
BUT I'M AFRAID
WE WERE JUST ON OUR WAY OUT.

20:11.631 --> 20:12.832
CARL HAS A CHECKUP.

20:12.832 --> 20:15.094
YOU CAN'T.
DAVID HAS TO MEET HIS GRANDSON.

20:15.094 --> 20:17.427
[ CARL COOING, TOY SQUEAKS ]

20:17.427 --> 20:19.339
OF COURSE.

20:19.339 --> 20:21.140
[ CARL LAUGHING ]

20:26.846 --> 20:28.808
[ Chuckling ] HEY.

20:30.109 --> 20:33.813
HEY THERE, BIG MAN.

20:33.813 --> 20:35.024
I'M YOUR GRANDPA.

20:36.406 --> 20:38.738
IT'S THE FIRST TIME
I'VE EVER SAID THAT.

20:38.738 --> 20:41.200
HE HAS HER EYES,
DON'T YOU THINK?

20:42.992 --> 20:45.535
IT'S HARD
FOR ME TO REMEMBER.

20:45.535 --> 20:47.126
I'LL GET
THE WEDDING ALBUM.

20:47.126 --> 20:48.958
THERE'S SOME GREAT CLOSEUP SHOTS
OF AMANDA. YOU'LL SEE IT.

20:52.872 --> 20:55.084
IT'S A NICE HOME YOU'VE MADE
FOR YOURSELF HERE, JACK.

20:55.084 --> 20:58.087
Charlotte: I JUST WISH AMANDA
COULD HAVE SEEN THIS PLACE.

20:58.087 --> 21:00.049
SHE ALWAYS WANTED
A HOUSE LIKE THIS.

21:00.049 --> 21:01.801
OH.

21:01.801 --> 21:03.433
WHERE DID YOU TWO LIVE?

21:04.974 --> 21:06.225
DOWN ON THE WATERFRONT.

21:06.225 --> 21:07.767
REMEMBER THE STOWAWAY?

21:07.767 --> 21:09.559
THE -- THE BAR?

21:09.559 --> 21:10.850
THEY LIVED ABOVE IT.

21:10.850 --> 21:14.153
IT WAS NICER THAN IT SOUNDS --
SMALL, BUT COZY.

21:14.153 --> 21:16.946
HERE'S AMANDA.

21:16.946 --> 21:19.198
OH, YEAH.

21:19.198 --> 21:20.950
HE DOES HAVE HER EYES.

21:20.950 --> 21:22.992
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:22.992 --> 21:24.784
I'M SORRY, GUYS.

21:24.784 --> 21:26.866
I REALLY NEED TO GET CARL
TO THIS DOCTOR'S APARTMENT.

21:26.866 --> 21:29.999
YEAH, OF COURSE.
JACK, THANK YOU SO MUCH.

21:29.999 --> 21:31.000
YOU KNOW,
IT'S CLEAR TO ME

21:31.000 --> 21:32.872
THAT YOU'VE GROWN UP
TO BE AN HONORABLE MAN.

21:35.004 --> 21:38.338
YEAH,
JACK'S ONE OF THE GOOD GUYS.

21:46.556 --> 21:48.558
[ ENGINE SHUTS OFF ]

21:50.430 --> 21:51.731
I COULD GET IN
A LOT OF TROUBLE

21:51.731 --> 21:52.932
IF SOMEONE FINDS OUT
I GAVE YOU THIS.

21:52.932 --> 21:54.934
YOU DON'T HAVE CLEARANCE, BEN.
IT'S A FEDERAL CASE.

21:54.934 --> 21:57.276
YEAH -- ONE THEY AREN'T
ANY CLOSER TO SOLVING, EITHER.

21:57.276 --> 22:00.610
FIGURE, WHY NOT
TAKE A SHOT AT IT MYSELF?

22:00.610 --> 22:03.282
AND MAKE DETECTIVE, RIGHT?
THAT MEAN YOU GOT A LEAD?

22:03.282 --> 22:05.244
I GOT A SUSPECT
WITH MOTIVE.

22:05.244 --> 22:06.996
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

22:11.080 --> 22:12.952
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:17.006 --> 22:19.298
DAVID.

22:19.298 --> 22:21.050
I WANT TO...TALK TO YOU.

22:21.050 --> 22:22.422
OF COURSE.

22:22.422 --> 22:24.964
COME IN. COME IN.

22:24.964 --> 22:26.466
NO...POLICE?

22:26.466 --> 22:29.559
NO, THEY'RE WAITING OUTSIDE.
I WANTED SOME PRIVACY.

22:30.810 --> 22:32.061
RIGHT.

22:32.061 --> 22:34.974
WELL, I-I KNEW YOU'D HAVE,
UH, QUESTIONS ABOUT AMANDA.

22:34.974 --> 22:39.399
DID YOU GIVE HER THE MONEY
OR THE BOX THAT I MADE HER?

22:39.399 --> 22:41.070
DID SHE EVER GET
THE JOURNALS?

22:41.070 --> 22:43.533
I GAVE HER EVERYTHING
THE DAY SHE GOT OUT --

22:43.533 --> 22:45.034
EVERYTHING THAT YOU ASKED.

22:45.034 --> 22:47.747
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:47.747 --> 22:50.079
THEN WHY WAS SHE LIVING
ABOVE A BAR?

22:50.079 --> 22:52.041
BECAUSE --

22:54.584 --> 22:56.956
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

22:56.956 --> 22:59.419
I KNOW.

22:59.419 --> 23:03.423
YOU'RE HEARING A LOT OF CRAZY
THINGS ABOUT AMANDA RIGHT NOW --

23:03.423 --> 23:06.926
SOME OF THEM FROM PEOPLE
YOU MAY EVEN THINK YOU TRUST.

23:08.057 --> 23:10.970
I HOPE YOU WON'T
TAKE THEIR WORD AS FACT.

23:10.970 --> 23:14.103
I HOPE
THAT YOU WILL TRUST

23:14.103 --> 23:18.187
WHAT YOU KNOW IN YOUR HEART
TO BE TRUE.

23:19.439 --> 23:22.021
BUT THAT'S THE PROBLEM,
NOLAN.

23:23.483 --> 23:26.235
SEE,
THE MORE I HEAR...

23:28.287 --> 23:32.411
...THE HARDER IT IS FOR ME
TO REMEMBER MY LITTLE GIRL.

23:34.954 --> 23:39.088
SHE'S SLIPPING AWAY
FROM ME.

23:39.088 --> 23:41.881
AND THAT
SCARES THE HELL OUT OF ME.

23:49.178 --> 23:50.720
[ SIGHS ]

23:57.977 --> 24:00.059
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]

24:00.059 --> 24:02.441
FIGURED YOU'D BE HERE.

24:04.984 --> 24:06.866
GUESS IT WAS A BAD DAY
ALL AROUND.

24:06.866 --> 24:10.029
I WENT TO SEE MY FATHER,

24:10.029 --> 24:12.572
AND VICTORIA
WAS WAITING FOR ME INSTEAD.

24:12.572 --> 24:14.163
[ SCOFFS ]

24:14.163 --> 24:15.995
I'M NOT THINKING THIS THROUGH
PROPERLY.

24:15.995 --> 24:18.077
NOLAN WAS RIGHT.
HE WARNED ME NOT TO GO.

24:18.077 --> 24:22.421
I DOUBT THERE'S A PERSON ALIVE
WHO COULD HAVE STOPPED YOU.

24:22.421 --> 24:24.133
WELL,
YOU'RE PROBABLY RIGHT.

24:26.966 --> 24:30.179
JACK, DO YOU THINK
MY FATHER'S GONNA HATE ME

24:30.179 --> 24:31.220
FOR EVERYTHING I'VE DONE?

24:31.220 --> 24:32.642
STOP IT.

24:32.642 --> 24:34.724
THAT'S JUST VICTORIA
GETTING INSIDE YOUR HEAD.

24:34.724 --> 24:35.765
NO, IT'S NOT.

24:35.765 --> 24:38.187
YOU NEED TO HAVE FAITH
IN HIM, EMILY.

24:38.187 --> 24:40.600
TRUST ME -- A FATHER
NEVER STOPS LOVING THEIR CHILD.

24:40.600 --> 24:43.943
PEOPLE DIED IN HIS NAME.

24:43.943 --> 24:46.155
MY FATHER NEVER
WOULD HAVE WANTED THAT.

24:46.155 --> 24:47.987
YES,
BUT THEY STARTED IT.

24:47.987 --> 24:50.029
YOU DID WHAT YOU HAD TO DO
TO STOP THEM.

24:50.029 --> 24:51.991
NO ONE KNOWS THAT
BETTER THAN ME.

24:51.991 --> 24:53.112
BECAUSE YOU WERE THERE.

24:53.112 --> 24:55.034
BUT HOW AM I GONNA GET HIM
TO UNDERSTAND

24:55.034 --> 24:56.325
IF I CAN'T EVEN
GET TO HIM?

24:56.325 --> 24:58.327
VICTORIA CAN TWIST THE TRUTH --
ALL OF IT.

24:58.327 --> 25:01.250
NO. SHE CAN'T.

25:01.250 --> 25:04.293
I KNOW,
'CAUSE I WAS JUST WITH DAVID.

25:04.293 --> 25:05.795
WHAT?
 YES.

25:05.795 --> 25:07.046
HE'S AFRAID --

25:07.046 --> 25:09.719
MAINLY OF LOSING TOUCH
WITH THE MEMORY OF YOU, EMILY.

25:09.719 --> 25:11.340
AND THE GOOD NEWS IS,

25:11.340 --> 25:13.012
HE HASN'T GIVEN UP
ON HIS DAUGHTER.

25:13.012 --> 25:16.435
THERE IS STILL A CHANCE
THAT YOU CAN CONNECT WITH HIM.

25:16.435 --> 25:18.097
YOU NEED TO GET DAVID
AWAY FROM HER.

25:19.639 --> 25:20.690
[ SIGHS ]

25:20.690 --> 25:22.061
I NEED TO BRING MY FATHER

25:22.061 --> 25:25.024
BACK TO A TIME
THAT VICTORIA CAN'T TOUCH --

25:25.024 --> 25:27.526
WHEN IT WAS JUST THE TWO OF US
IN THIS HOUSE.

25:30.149 --> 25:32.531
MY FATHER NEEDS
AMANDA CLARKE.

25:40.660 --> 25:42.582
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

25:42.582 --> 25:44.293
IF YOU'VE COME HERE
TO DO BATTLE,

25:44.293 --> 25:46.085
I MUST WARN YOU --
I HAVE AN 11:30,

25:46.085 --> 25:47.216
SO PLEASE BE CONCISE.

25:47.216 --> 25:49.128
I AM NOT HERE
TO ARGUE.

25:49.128 --> 25:52.131
IN FACT, I CAME
TO APOLOGIZE FOR YESTERDAY.

25:52.131 --> 25:55.935
I DON'T ALWAYS THINK CLEARLY
WHEN IT COMES TO AMANDA.

25:55.935 --> 25:57.226
THEN LET ME ASSURE YOU --

25:57.226 --> 26:00.179
I HAVE NO INTEREST
IN EXPLOITING HER FATHER.

26:00.179 --> 26:02.732
I KNOW.

26:02.732 --> 26:04.894
YOU'RE A GOOD PERSON,
MARGAUX.

26:04.894 --> 26:07.486
THAT BECAME CLEAR TO ME
WHEN YOU CUT TIES WITH DANIEL.

26:08.948 --> 26:12.451
SO, WHAT BRINGS YOU BY,
EMILY?

26:12.451 --> 26:14.573
I WANT TO DO SOMETHING
FOR DAVID --

26:14.573 --> 26:16.996
SOMETHING THAT I BELIEVE
WILL AID IN HIS RECOVERY

26:16.996 --> 26:19.288
AND MIGHT ALSO GIVE YOU

26:19.288 --> 26:22.121
A WAY AROUND
VICTORIA'S MEDIA BLACKOUT.

26:22.121 --> 26:24.914
FORGIVE ME,
BUT HOW WOULD THAT WORK?

26:24.914 --> 26:26.505
YOU AND VICTORIA
SEEM TO HAVE QUI--

26:26.505 --> 26:28.127
A STRAINED RELATIONSHIP?

26:28.127 --> 26:30.169
THAT'S A NICE WAY
OF PUTTING IT.

26:30.169 --> 26:32.171
WELL, SEE,
THAT'S WHERE YOU COME IN.

26:32.171 --> 26:34.674
OBVIOUSLY, VICTORIA WOULD NEVER
ACCEPT A GESTURE FROM ME,

26:34.674 --> 26:37.176
SO IT'S VITAL THAT MY NAME
BE KEPT OUT OF THE STORY --

26:37.176 --> 26:40.850
THAT IS, IF YOU'RE WILLING
TO TAKE FULL CREDIT.

26:44.023 --> 26:45.645
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

26:48.988 --> 26:51.110
I WAS WONDERING
WHEN YOU'D SHOW UP.

26:51.110 --> 26:52.692
WANT A DRINK?

26:52.692 --> 26:55.614
WHAT THE HELL DO YOU THINK
YOU WERE PULLING YESTERDAY?

26:58.738 --> 27:01.620
WOW. YOU ARE NOT
A VERY GOOD COP.

27:01.620 --> 27:03.242
TERRIBLE
DEDUCTIVE REASONING.

27:03.242 --> 27:05.164
SO THIS IS ALL
JUST SOME SICK JOKE

27:05.164 --> 27:06.666
TO YOU AND YOUR MOTHER --
IS THAT IT?

27:06.666 --> 27:08.457
NO. SHE HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH MY VISIT.

27:08.457 --> 27:09.959
WHAT IF I'D TOLD DAVID
THE TRUTH?

27:09.959 --> 27:11.630
AND EXPOSE EMILY?

27:11.630 --> 27:13.843
NOT A CHANCE.

27:13.843 --> 27:17.216
YOU'RE A COWARD, JACK --
A JOKE.

27:20.680 --> 27:22.021
WE'RE DONE HERE.

27:24.974 --> 27:26.726
YOU KNOW,
I CAME HERE THINKING

27:26.726 --> 27:30.029
YOU WERE JUST SOME KID
PRETENDING TO BE HER MOTHER.

27:30.029 --> 27:32.361
YOU'RE NOT VICTORIA.
YOU'RE WORSE.

27:32.361 --> 27:33.482
YOU'RE CONRAD.

27:33.482 --> 27:36.035
I'M NOTHING LIKE HIM.

27:36.035 --> 27:37.366
YOU'RE DOING
EXACTLY WHAT HE DID.

27:37.366 --> 27:38.948
YOU ARE TORTURING DAVID.
AND FOR WHAT?

27:38.948 --> 27:40.700
SOME PATHETIC POWER TRIP
OVER ME?

27:40.700 --> 27:41.781
HE'S YOUR FATHER,
CHARLOTTE.

27:45.124 --> 27:49.048
NO WONDER YOU HAVE TO HIDE
BEHIND ALL THAT CRAP.

27:49.048 --> 27:50.790
HOW ELSE
COULD YOU LIVE WITH YOURSELF?

27:56.055 --> 27:58.888
Ben: YOU WORKED
THE GRAYSON KIDNAPPING, RIGHT?

27:58.888 --> 28:01.931
YEAH. I WAS THERE
WHEN PORTER GOT ARRESTED.

28:01.931 --> 28:03.142
WHY YOU ASKING?

28:03.142 --> 28:04.013
WELL, HE'S MY PARTNER.

28:04.013 --> 28:06.145
JUST WANT TO KNOW
WHAT KIND OF MAN HE IS.

28:06.145 --> 28:07.897
AND YOU WERE THERE
FOR THE QUESTIONING?

28:07.897 --> 28:09.228
[ SCOFFS ] OH, YEAH.

28:09.228 --> 28:11.020
YEAH, REYES GRILLED HIM
FOR HOURS.

28:11.020 --> 28:12.611
SHE WAS SURE
HE WAS GUILTY.

28:12.611 --> 28:14.363
SHE FIGURED
PORTER PLANNED IT ALL --

28:14.363 --> 28:15.945
YOU KNOW,
GRABBED THE GIRL,

28:15.945 --> 28:19.028
PLANTED THE CAMERA ON HER,
TOOK GRAYSON DOWN.

28:19.028 --> 28:19.989
I NEVER BOUGHT IT.

28:19.989 --> 28:21.240
WHY NOT?

28:21.240 --> 28:23.242
I MEAN, GRAYSON KILLED
HIS WIFE AND HIS BROTHER.

28:23.242 --> 28:24.703
[ SCOFFS ]

28:24.703 --> 28:27.086
WHOEVER PULLED THAT OFF WASN'T
THE OWNER OF SOME DIVE BAR.

28:27.086 --> 28:28.457
AN OPERATION LIKE THAT
TAKES MONEY.

28:31.130 --> 28:33.172
SO YOU NEVER LOOKED AT PORTER
FOR THE MURDER, HUH?

28:34.794 --> 28:37.797
HE WAS IN WITH REYES AND ME
WHEN GRAYSON GOT WHACKED.

28:37.797 --> 28:39.298
BEST ALIBI
A GUY COULD HAVE.

28:41.180 --> 28:42.972
RIGHT.

28:42.972 --> 28:44.764
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

28:44.764 --> 28:47.146
DANIEL? ARE YOU HERE?

28:47.146 --> 28:48.017
HEY.

28:48.017 --> 28:50.439
YOU HAVEN'T BEEN RETURNING
ANY OF MY CALLS.

28:50.439 --> 28:51.520
I'M WORKING.

28:51.520 --> 28:52.982
WELL,
I MAY HAVE SOMETHING

28:52.982 --> 28:55.945
THAT CAN HELP YOU
EVEN MORE THAN LOUISE ELLIS.

28:55.945 --> 28:58.407
MARGAUX, I DON'T ASK ABOUT
 YOUR WORK, SO STAY OUT OF MINE.

29:00.739 --> 29:03.913
DON'T PUSH ME AWAY --
NOT THIS TIME.

29:03.913 --> 29:05.164
YOU MAY NOT SEE IT YET,

29:05.164 --> 29:08.037
BUT I KNOW WE'RE BETTER TOGETHER
THAN APART.

29:08.037 --> 29:11.000
I WOULD HAVE NEVER BEEN ABLE
TO TAKE ON GIDEON WITHOUT YOU.

29:11.000 --> 29:12.541
AND NOW
I HAVE FOUND A WAY

29:12.541 --> 29:15.374
TO PUT YOUR FATHER'S SCANDAL
BEHIND YOU --

29:15.374 --> 29:17.336
FOREVER.

29:17.336 --> 29:18.968
BUT YOU HAVE TO TRUST ME.

29:18.968 --> 29:23.432
WHATEVER YOU GOT TO DO,
JUST DO IT WITHOUT ME.

29:23.432 --> 29:25.594
DANIEL,
THIS ISN'T CHARITY.

29:25.594 --> 29:27.596
IT'S SIMPLY
GOOD BUSINESS --

29:27.596 --> 29:29.558
FOR BOTH OF US.

29:37.106 --> 29:39.108
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

29:40.659 --> 29:41.861
WHERE ARE THE POLICE?

29:43.162 --> 29:45.034
I SENT THEM AWAY.
I DON'T WANT THEM ANYMORE.

29:45.034 --> 29:48.077
THEY STILL HAVEN'T FOUND
THE DRIVER OF THAT CAR, DAVID.

29:48.077 --> 29:49.578
IT'S TOO DANGEROUS.

29:49.578 --> 29:51.210
I WAS A PRISONER
FOR 20 YEARS.

29:51.210 --> 29:53.042
I WON'T LIVE LIKE ONE
ANYMORE.

29:53.042 --> 29:53.963
DAVID.

29:56.005 --> 29:59.178
DAVID, TRUST ME WHEN I TELL YOU
THAT YOU NEED THEIR PROTECTION.

29:59.178 --> 30:01.800
NOT EVERYBODY HERE HAS
YOUR BEST INTERESTS AT HEART.

30:01.800 --> 30:03.222
Y-YOU'RE NOT
THE FIRST PERSON

30:03.222 --> 30:05.054
TO SAY SOMETHING LIKE THAT
TO ME.

30:05.054 --> 30:08.848
AND IT'S, UH...
MAKING ME WONDER

30:08.848 --> 30:12.351
WHO I CAN TRUST
AND WHO I SHOULDN'T.

30:12.351 --> 30:14.433
SOMETHING IS NOT RIGHT
HERE.

30:14.433 --> 30:16.936
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

30:27.536 --> 30:29.038
MR. CLARKE.

30:29.038 --> 30:31.080
DANIEL? [ CHUCKLES ]
GOD, LOOK AT YOU.

30:31.080 --> 30:35.004
DANIEL, THIS ISN'T
A GOOD TIME RIGHT NOW.

30:35.004 --> 30:38.047
LISTEN, I'M, UH...

30:38.047 --> 30:40.259
SORRY TO STOP BY
UNANNOUNCED.

30:40.259 --> 30:42.171
I JUST NEEDED
TO COME HERE TODAY

30:42.171 --> 30:45.634
TO PERSONALLY APOLOGIZE
FOR WHAT WAS DONE TO YOU.

30:45.634 --> 30:46.886
YOU WEREN'T RESPONSIBLE.

30:46.886 --> 30:50.019
NO, STILL, WHAT MY FATHER DID
DEFIES WORDS,

30:50.019 --> 30:52.771
AND REPARATIONS
NEED TO BE MADE.

30:52.771 --> 30:54.773
THAT'S THE DEED
TO YOUR BEACH HOUSE.

30:54.773 --> 30:57.526
CONSIDER IT
MY GIFT TO YOU.

30:59.568 --> 31:01.110
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

31:01.110 --> 31:02.651
ATONING
FOR MY FATHER'S SINS.

31:02.651 --> 31:06.245
DAVID, I'VE ALREADY LINED UP
A PLACE FOR US.

31:06.245 --> 31:07.947
THIS WAS MY HOME.

31:07.947 --> 31:10.039
THIS --
THIS IS WHAT I WANT.

31:21.210 --> 31:23.462
[ SWITCH CLICKS ]

31:39.979 --> 31:42.151
EMILY WOULD NEVER
SELL TO YOU.

31:42.151 --> 31:43.822
NOW, HOW DID YOU GET THE DEED
TO THIS HOUSE?

31:43.822 --> 31:45.654
SHE DIDN'T KNOW
I WAS INVOLVED.

31:45.654 --> 31:47.406
I REFUSE TO ALLOW YOU
TO USE DAVID.

31:47.406 --> 31:49.368
SEE, I THOUGHT
YOU MIGHT SAY THAT,

31:49.368 --> 31:50.950
SO I TOOK
A FEW PRECAUTIONS.

31:57.166 --> 31:59.588
CAT'S OUT OF THE BAG NOW.

31:59.588 --> 32:01.800
JUST SMILE
FOR THE CAMERAS.

32:01.800 --> 32:04.303
DON'T WANT TO CAUSE A SCENE,
DO YOU?

32:04.303 --> 32:06.805
DAVID. HEY,
THIS IS MARGAUX LeMARCHAL.

32:06.805 --> 32:08.007
SHE HEADS UP...

32:08.007 --> 32:10.009
LeMARCHAL MEDIA.
YES, I-I KNOW WHO SHE IS.

32:10.009 --> 32:11.971
UH...DO YOU MIND
EXPLAINING THE CAMERAS?

32:11.971 --> 32:14.813
WELL, DANIEL THOUGHT
WE COULD CONTAIN THE GOSSIP

32:14.813 --> 32:18.227
IF SOMEONE HE TRUSTED
COVERED THIS STORY.

32:21.820 --> 32:23.062
LET'S JUST GO OUTSIDE.

32:23.062 --> 32:24.113
NO, IT WON'T TAKE LONG.

32:24.113 --> 32:26.945
DAVID, ARE YOU COMFORTABLE
WITH THIS?

32:26.945 --> 32:29.118
I AM.

32:29.118 --> 32:30.739
Margaux:
JUST STICK TO THE QUESTIONS.

32:30.739 --> 32:33.162
THEN I'M HAPPY FOR YOU.

32:33.162 --> 32:35.034
THIS IS YOUR HOME.

32:49.088 --> 32:50.299
[ NOLAN SIGHS ]

32:50.299 --> 32:53.182
YOU GOT YOUR FATHER
AWAY FROM VICTORIA.

32:53.182 --> 32:57.646
ALTHOUGH DANIEL AND MARGAUX
IS A TWIST I DIDN'T SEE COMING.

32:57.646 --> 33:00.479
NOW I KNOW
MARGAUX ISN'T TRULY AN ALLY.

33:00.479 --> 33:02.561
SHE REALLY IS
HER FATHER'S DAUGHTER.

33:02.561 --> 33:06.025
OH, SHACKING UP WITH THE SON
OF KONG-RAD, NO LESS.

33:06.025 --> 33:07.526
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:07.526 --> 33:09.608
SO,
WHAT DO WE CALL THEM?

33:09.608 --> 33:11.030
MaNiel?

33:11.030 --> 33:12.991
MM. DanGaux?

33:14.203 --> 33:16.165
TROUBLE.

33:32.091 --> 33:35.594
THAT PARLOR TRICK YOU PULLED
WITH DANIEL TONIGHT

33:35.594 --> 33:37.096
DISAPPOINTED ME, MARGAUX.

33:37.096 --> 33:39.058
OH, I'M SORRY
YOU FEEL THAT WAY.

33:39.058 --> 33:42.561
I WILL NOT ALLOW YOU
TO USE DAVID LIKE THAT AGAIN.

33:42.561 --> 33:45.854
WELL, THEN, PERHAPS WE SHOULD
COME TO AN ARRANGEMENT --

33:45.854 --> 33:49.608
ONE WITH LESS OPPORTUNITY
FOR SURPRISES.

33:49.608 --> 33:52.911
GIVE ME EXCLUSIVE RIGHTS
TO DAVID'S STORY.

33:52.911 --> 33:55.204
CONSIDER IT
REPAYMENT OF YOUR DEBT.

33:55.204 --> 33:57.076
I CAN'T SPEAK FOR DAVID,
MARGAUX.

33:57.076 --> 33:58.367
YOU KNOW BETTER
THAN THAT.

33:58.367 --> 34:01.790
BUT I MAY BE ABLE TO FACILITATE
SUCH AN ARRANGEMENT

34:01.790 --> 34:04.793
PROVIDED YOU GIVE US
FINAL APPROVAL ON ALL STORIES.

34:04.793 --> 34:07.005
I CANNOT DO THAT.

34:07.005 --> 34:09.967
WELL,
THAT'S UNFORTUNATE.

34:09.967 --> 34:14.052
AS YOU KNOW, YOUR COMPETITORS
HAVE APPROACHED ME.

34:14.052 --> 34:16.304
WHO KNOWS WHAT ONE
OF THE MORE TENACIOUS REPORTERS

34:16.304 --> 34:20.179
MIGHT UNCOVER
IN THEIR OWN INVESTIGATION --

34:20.179 --> 34:23.562
MAYBE EVEN YOUR FAMILY'S
CONNECTION TO THE SCANDAL.

34:23.562 --> 34:27.646
AND LACKING ANY PERSONAL
RELATIONSHIP WITH THEM,

34:27.646 --> 34:30.109
I MAY BE POWERLESS
TO STOP IT.

34:30.109 --> 34:32.741
YOU WOULD NEVER
ALLOW ANYONE

34:32.741 --> 34:35.244
TO TARNISH THE MEMORY
OF YOUR PASCAL.

34:35.244 --> 34:37.156
PERHAPS YOU'RE RIGHT.

34:37.156 --> 34:40.409
DO FEEL FREE
TO CALL MY BLUFF.

34:42.791 --> 34:44.793
[ SETS GLASS DOWN ]

34:46.043 --> 34:47.045
VICTORIA.

34:49.047 --> 34:51.009
WE HAVE A DEAL.

34:58.307 --> 35:00.679
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]
 OH, NO, NO.
IT'S THE LEAST THAT I COULD DO.

35:00.679 --> 35:02.561
I MEAN, POOR GUY
HAS REALLY SUFFERED.

35:02.561 --> 35:05.023
WELL, YEAH,
I'D LOVE TO MEET TOMORROW.

35:06.985 --> 35:08.857
KEITH,
LET ME CALL YOU BACK.

35:10.819 --> 35:13.942
SAW YOU ON TV
WITH THAT LeMARCHAL GIRL.

35:13.942 --> 35:16.155
YOU TWO LOOKED COZY.

35:16.155 --> 35:19.998
SO I ASKED AROUND,
AND THE CONCIERGE SAYS

35:19.998 --> 35:22.040
SHE'S BEEN SNEAKING UP HERE
FOR DAYS.

35:22.040 --> 35:25.083
YOU LIED TO ME, DANIEL.

35:26.665 --> 35:29.748
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

35:29.748 --> 35:31.630
YOU'RE RIGHT.

35:31.630 --> 35:33.922
I DID LIE TO YOU.

35:33.922 --> 35:35.674
AND TO MYSELF.

35:35.674 --> 35:37.676
YOU WERE RIGHT ABOUT ME,
LOUISE.

35:37.676 --> 35:40.389
I'VE BEEN TRYING
TO FIGURE OUT WHO I AM.

35:40.389 --> 35:42.140
AND FOR A MINUTE,
I THOUGHT I COULD BE

35:42.140 --> 35:44.973
THE GUY I WAS WITH YOU
YESTERDAY, BUT...

35:44.973 --> 35:48.146
TODAY, I WAS REMINDED
THAT I'M PART OF A TEAM,

35:48.146 --> 35:49.608
AND WE'RE DAMN GOOD
TOGETHER.

35:49.608 --> 35:52.321
AND WHAT DOES THAT MEAN
FOR ME?

35:52.321 --> 35:55.694
WELL, YOU HIRED ME TO
PROTECT YOU AND YOUR INTERESTS,

35:55.694 --> 35:58.156
SO THAT'S WHAT I PLAN ON DOING
FROM NOW ON.

35:58.156 --> 36:00.038
UNLESS YOU'RE NOT COMFORTABLE
WITH ME,

36:00.038 --> 36:05.123
AND IF THAT'S THE CASE,
THEN WE'LL GO OUR SEPARATE WAYS.

36:05.123 --> 36:06.745
IT'S YOUR CALL.

36:06.745 --> 36:08.747
[ SIGHS ]

36:15.133 --> 36:16.755
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]

36:16.755 --> 36:18.467
WHY WOULD I GO WITH ANYONE
BUT YOU?

36:18.467 --> 36:21.059
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

36:21.059 --> 36:22.931
FANTASTIC.

36:22.931 --> 36:28.267
LISTEN, WE ARE GONNA MAKE
A TON OF MONEY TOGETHER, LOUISE.

36:28.267 --> 36:31.570
TOMORROW,
YOU AND I START OVER.

36:31.570 --> 36:33.732
WE KEEP THINGS
STRICTLY PROFESSIONAL.

36:33.732 --> 36:35.113
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

36:35.113 --> 36:38.156
AND TRUST ME --
I'M DOING YOU A FAVOR.

36:38.156 --> 36:40.659
I MEAN, YOU REALLY DON'T WANT
TO BE A PART OF MY FAMILY.

36:48.537 --> 36:50.168
[ ELEVATOR WHIRS ]

36:50.168 --> 36:51.169
[ SIGHS ]

36:55.093 --> 36:58.176
[ GRUNTING ]

36:58.176 --> 37:00.259
[ SIGHS ]

37:07.846 --> 37:11.109
[ DIALING ]

37:11.109 --> 37:12.771
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

37:12.771 --> 37:14.853
YES, HELLO.

37:14.853 --> 37:16.985
PLEASE CONNECT ME TO PAGE SIX.

37:16.985 --> 37:20.238
I HAVE A STORY
ABOUT DANIEL GRAYSON.

37:25.324 --> 37:27.326
DID YOU THINK
YOU COULD PULL THAT FILE

37:27.326 --> 37:29.167
WITHOUT MY FINDING OUT?

37:30.579 --> 37:31.920
YOU'RE A BEAT COP,
HUNTER.

37:31.920 --> 37:33.502
YOU GOT NO BUSINESS
KICKING THAT NEST.

37:33.502 --> 37:35.133
YEAH, WELL,
SOMEONE SHOULD, CHIEF.

37:35.133 --> 37:36.585
COME ON --
CONRAD GRAYSON GETS KILLED

37:36.585 --> 37:38.967
DAYS AFTER BEING EXPOSED
FOR MASTERMINDING FLIGHT 197,

37:38.967 --> 37:41.880
AND THE CASE
IS STILL OPEN?

37:41.880 --> 37:45.093
SO...
 YOU CLOSE IT?

37:45.093 --> 37:47.436
NO.
MY SUSPECT HAS AN ALIBI.

37:47.436 --> 37:50.148
I GET YOU'RE HUNGRY, BEN.
I REALLY DO.

37:50.148 --> 37:52.771
AND SOMEDAY,
YOU'LL MAKE DETECTIVE,

37:52.771 --> 37:56.695
BUT IT WILL NOT BE
ON THIS CASE.

37:56.695 --> 37:59.658
NOW...
HAND OVER THE FILE.

38:07.115 --> 38:08.286
TRUST ME --

38:08.286 --> 38:11.249
NOTHING GOOD
COMES FROM THIS.

38:32.060 --> 38:34.893
DADDY!!
 YOU'RE MAKING A MISTAKE!
YOU'RE MAKING A MISTAKE!!

38:34.893 --> 38:36.064
[ SCREAMING ]

38:36.064 --> 38:38.026
LET GO OF HER!
LEAVE HER ALONE!

39:00.799 --> 39:02.461
TO YOUR FATHER'S
RETURN HOME.

39:02.461 --> 39:03.592
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:03.592 --> 39:05.424
SO, WHEN ARE YOU
GONNA TELL HIM?

39:08.016 --> 39:09.177
WHEN HE'S READY.

39:09.177 --> 39:10.889
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:10.889 --> 39:12.180
WHY WAIT?

39:12.180 --> 39:14.683
I THOUGHT THAT WAS THE WHOLE
POINT OF GETTING HIM NEXT DOOR.

39:14.683 --> 39:17.315
THIS ISN'T ABOUT ME, NOLAN.
IT'S ABOUT HELPING HIM.

39:17.315 --> 39:20.689
AFTER WHAT HE'S BEEN THROUGH,
MY FATHER NEEDS TIME TO RECOVER.

39:23.241 --> 39:27.075
I WANT TO WIN HIM BACK
HONESTLY -- WITH THE TRUTH.

39:27.075 --> 39:29.197
AND WHEN HE'S READY,
I'LL MAKE SURE THAT HE KNOWS

39:29.197 --> 39:31.790
THAT...
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

39:31.790 --> 39:33.992
I'M STILL HERE.
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:33.992 --> 39:36.995
[ HARRY NILSSON'S
"EVERYBODY'S TALKIN'" PLAYS ]

39:42.591 --> 39:46.925
♪ EVERYBODY'S TALKIN' AT ME ♪

39:46.925 --> 39:49.387
♪ I DON'T HEAR
A WORD THEY'RE SAYIN' ♪

39:49.387 --> 39:51.720
WE USED TO DANCE TO THIS.

39:51.720 --> 39:53.932
♪ ONLY THE ECHOES OF MY MIND ♪

39:53.932 --> 39:55.564
IT WAS HIS FAVORITE.

39:58.316 --> 40:02.190
♪ PEOPLE STOPPIN', STARIN' ♪

40:02.190 --> 40:06.024
♪ I CAN'T SEE THEIR FACES ♪

40:06.024 --> 40:11.079
♪ ONLY THE SHADOWS
OF THEIR EYES ♪

40:13.081 --> 40:15.994
♪ I'M GOIN'
WHERE THE SUN KEEPS SHININ' ♪

40:15.994 --> 40:17.375
[ GIGGLES ]

40:17.375 --> 40:18.376
ARE YOU READY?

40:18.376 --> 40:20.839
♪ THROUGH THE POURIN' RAIN ♪

40:20.839 --> 40:27.345
♪ GOIN' WHERE THE WEATHER
SUITS MY CLOTHES ♪

40:27.345 --> 40:30.469
Nolan: HOW DID SHE GET THIS SONG
TO PLAY ON CUE?

40:30.469 --> 40:32.851
REMOTE CONTROL?
MOTION SENSOR?

40:32.851 --> 40:35.103
♪ SAILIN' ON A SUMMER BREEZE ♪

40:35.103 --> 40:36.144
SHE DIDN'T NEED
ANY OF THAT.

40:36.144 --> 40:37.976
♪ AND SKIPPIN' OVER THE OCEAN ♪

40:37.976 --> 40:39.768
SHE JUST HAD TO GET HIM
BACK HOME.

40:39.768 --> 40:42.110
♪ LIKE A STONE ♪

40:43.982 --> 40:47.325
♪ WHOA, WHOA-WHOA-WHOA ♪

40:47.325 --> 40:49.988
♪ WHOA, WHOA, WHOA... ♪

40:49.988 --> 40:51.069
[ LAUGHTER ]

40:51.069 --> 40:53.532
[ DANCE MUSIC PLAYS ]

40:53.532 --> 40:56.204
WHAT DID YOU SAY
YOUR NAME WAS, AGAIN?

40:56.204 --> 40:58.877
OH, NEVER MIND.
IT DOESN'T MATTER.

40:58.877 --> 41:01.079
YOU'RE GOING PRETTY HARD
TONIGHT.

41:01.079 --> 41:03.081
I DON'T WANT TO THINK
ANYTHING.

41:03.081 --> 41:04.883
I DON'T WANT TO FEEL
ANYTHING.

41:04.883 --> 41:06.545
WELL, IN THAT CASE,

41:06.545 --> 41:09.297
I GOT JUST WHAT YOU NEED
BACK AT MY PLACE.

41:09.297 --> 41:12.260
THEN, WHAT ARE WE
STILL DOING HERE?

41:12.260 --> 41:14.763
NEVER THOUGHT I'D BE GOING HOME
WITH CHARLOTTE GRAYSON.

41:14.763 --> 41:16.474
David:
 I HAVE COME TO LEARN...

41:16.474 --> 41:17.596
IT'S "CLARKE."

41:17.596 --> 41:21.940
...THAT EVIL TAKES
MANY FORMS...

41:21.940 --> 41:23.151
MY MISTAKE.

41:29.948 --> 41:33.782
...INCLUDING THOSE THAT WE
THINK WE CAN TRUST THE MOST.

41:40.789 --> 41:42.961
THE ANGER THIS BRED
ALMOST COST ME

41:42.961 --> 41:47.425
THE THING THAT I VALUED
ABOVE ALL ELSE --

41:47.425 --> 41:50.468
MY MEMORIES OF YOU,

41:50.468 --> 41:56.134
THE DAUGHTER I STILL LOVE
INFINITY TIMES INFINITY.

41:56.134 --> 41:59.017
BUT NOW I CAN FEEL YOU AGAIN,

41:59.017 --> 42:03.021
WHICH IS WHY I KNOW
WHAT I MUST DO,

42:03.021 --> 42:06.144
